title: 820-00923 no power
message:
This arrived with liquid damage in the U3200 area. I have replaced U3200 and check all traces/resistors in the area. Everything measures good.

There seems to be a issue with PP3V3_G3H at C3200. Diode mode measures 0.581 on C3200 however measures normally at C3100 at 0.340. Amp Meter does not light up when trying to use U3200 . C3200 was replaced but no change.

What should be checked next??

title: 820-00923 no power
message:
3V3_G3H is unique for all CD3215 chips.
So you have broken/corroded trace somewhere.
